      <title>耶伦认为商业房地产面临更多压力和损失，但没有系统性银行风险</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/yellen-sees-more-commercial-real-estate-stress-losses-no-systemic-banking-risk-2024-02-08/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部长珍妮特·耶伦周四表示，她预计商业房地产市场疲软将带来额外的银行压力和财务损失，但相信这不会对银行体系构成系统性风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/yellen-sees-more-commercial-real-estate-stress-losses-no-systemic-banking-risk-2024-02-08/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 18:02:46 GMT</pubDate>
