      <title>美国炼油商击败华尔街押注，预计 2024 年需求将增长</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/us-oil-refiners-beat-wall-street-bets-expect-demand-grow-2024-2024-02-08/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国主要燃料制造商第四季度凭借强劲的炼油利润和运营业绩超出了华尔街的盈利预期，他们预计由于全球需求增长，今年利润将再次上升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/us-oil-refiners-beat-wall-street-bets-expect-demand-grow-2024-2024-02-08/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 18:01:57 GMT</pubDate>
