      <title>钯金价格自 2018 年以来首次跌破铂金</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/palladium-price-drops-below-platinum-first-time-since-2018-2024-02-08/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，现货钯金价格自 2018 年 4 月以来首次跌破姊妹金属铂金价格，因日益增长的需求担忧和对稳定供应的押注打压了该金属。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/palladium-price-drops-below-platinum-first-time-since-2018-2024-02-08/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 17:56:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
