      <title>大众汽车高管坚持北美电动汽车计划</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-sticking-with-north-american-ev-plans-executive-2024-02-08/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大众汽车北美业务负责人 Pablo Di Si 周四对路透社表示，大众汽车坚持到 2030 年在北美推出集团品牌 25 款电动汽车的计划，但准备随着市场的变化进行调整。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-sticking-with-north-american-ev-plans-executive-2024-02-08/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 17:36:36 GMT</pubDate>
